{"article_id":"jeN5DuKRBB8TqqZU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FERGUSON , Mo . -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"St. Louis County prosecutors plan to begin presenting evidence Wednesday to a local grand jury as part of an investigation into the fatal shooting of Michael Brown ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"a spokesman said Tuesday .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Edward Magee , spokesman for St. Louis County Prosecuting Attorney Robert McCulloch , said","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"local investigators have interviewed Ferguson police Officer Darren Wilson","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"and he will be `` offered the opportunity ''","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"to testify","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"if he chooses .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Magee said","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"the case will be presented to a regular grand jury","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that already has been seated .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"the panel has a few weeks remaining in its current term .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"He did not know","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"how long it would take","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"to present the case .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Attorney General Eric Holder on Tuesday promised a `` fair and thorough '' investigation into the fatal shooting of Brown , an 18-year-old African American , in an op-ed for the St. Louis Post-Dispatch in advance of his trip to Ferguson on Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"`` Since the Aug. 9 shooting death of Michael Brown , the nation and the world have witnessed the unrest","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that has gripped Ferguson , Mo , ''","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Holder wrote .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"`` At the core of these demonstrations is a demand for answers about the circumstances of this young man 's death and a broader concern about the state of our criminal justice system . ''","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Holder said","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"he was traveling to the city","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"to be briefed on the federal civil rights inquiry .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"He said","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"`` hundreds '' of potential witnesses have been interviewed ,","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"He cautioned","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"that the inquiry will `` take time","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"to complete . ''","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"`` At a time","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"when so much may seem uncertain ,","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"the people of Ferguson can have confidence","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"that the Justice Department intends to learn","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"- in a fair and thorough manner -","depth":13},{"id":34,"text":"exactly what happened , ''","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"Holder wrote .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` Approximately 40 FBI agents and some of the Civil Rights Division 's most experienced prosecutors have been deployed","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"to lead this process , ''","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"the attorney general said ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"that the federal autopsy","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"he called for over the weekend","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"was completed Monday .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"As with the family 's examination , additional investigation is needed","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"to determine critical facts ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"including whether Brown was facing the officer","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"when he was shot","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"and the distance between Brown and the officer at the time of the shooting .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"Holder said","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"he hopes","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"the federal investigation will bring a measure of calm to Ferguson .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"He called for `` an end to the acts of violence . ''","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"He also called on police to help reduce tensions","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"and regain the community 's trust .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Missouri State Attorney General Chris Koster visited West Florissant Avenue shortly after sunset Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"and announced to a group of protesters","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that a grand jury would be convening at 9 a.m. Wednesday CST .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"`` My understanding is that two senior prosecutors are going to bring the matter before a grand jury","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"-- one of whom is an African American woman , ''","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"`` My prayers are with them","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"that they do a great job . ''","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Koster said","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"he visited Ferguson","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"because it is important for elected officials to `` recognize the frustration","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that is being expressed","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"and come out","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"and interact","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"and talk with people in the community . ''","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Koster said ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"`` These folks are my bosses .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"I work for them . ''","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Meanwhile , as another night began in Ferguson","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"hundreds of protesters continued to demonstrate ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"many marching up and down West Florissant Avenue .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Things remained calm until just before midnight","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"when a glass bottle was thrown at police .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Police then ordered the protesters to disperse","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"and rushed into the crowd in pursuit of a suspect .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"One tense moment came","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"when police forced protesters out of a parking lot .","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"After initially resisting ,","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"the demonstrators moved back onto the sidewalks .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Police instructed protesters","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that they must keep the march moving","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"and told those","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"who did not wish to keep walking","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"that they could rest in the media staging area .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"`` I 'm not here for exercise , ''","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"one protester yelled at police ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Local leaders issued a statement","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"pleading for calm","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"and promising changes in the police department","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"as the city braced for another night of protests and possible confrontation .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"`` We plan to learn from this tragedy , ''","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"city officials said in the statement .","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"Officials are working to increase the number of black law enforcement applicants and raise funds for cameras for patrol car dashboards and officer vests ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"the statement said .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"Ten days of protests and violence are taking their toll on this normally quiet St.Louis suburb of 21,000 people .","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"`` This has to stop , ''","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Missouri State Highway Patrol Capt . Ron Johnson said Tuesday .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Johnson is tasked with bringing peace to a city","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"torn apart by violence","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"since Brown , 18 , was shot by Wilson , 28 ,","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"setting off angry protests","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"that have made international headlines .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Brown 's funeral will be Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"family lawyer Benjamin Crump said .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Also Tuesday , a 23-year-old man was fatally shot by a police officer in north St. Louis , just a few miles from Ferguson .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"Authorities said","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"he had threatened officers with a knife","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"and implored them to kill him .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Dozens of people milled about Tuesday night the area","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"where the man was shot ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"waving signs","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"and chanting ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"`` Hands up !","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"Shoot back ! ''","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"There 's a fairly heavy police contingent of about a dozen city police officers","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"but they 're staying in the background .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"At one point Tuesday evening , the proprietors of one of the businesses in the strip mall near the shooting drove up in a U-Haul truck ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"loaded up furniture , a television and other items from the business ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"and left .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"The relative quiet in Ferguson Tuesday comes","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"hours after peaceful demonstrations once again descended into chaos overnight .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Police said","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"they came `` under heavy gunfire ''","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"and arrested 78 people .","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"Johnson said","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"four police officers were injured by thrown rocks and bottles ,","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"at least two people were shot","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"and two fires were set during another night of clashes between police and protesters","depth":15},{"id":132,"text":"that lasted into early Tuesday .","depth":15},{"id":133,"text":"Johnson lauded local police , state troopers and National Guard personnel ,","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"they `` acted with restraint and calm . ''","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"police were shot at","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"but did not fire any shots themselves .","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"`` I do n't want anyone to get hurt .","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"I do n't want an officer to get hurt ,","depth":16},{"id":141,"text":"I do n't want a citizen to get hurt .","depth":16},{"id":142,"text":"We have to find a way","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"to stop it , ''","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"Even in daylight hours , life has not returned to normal .","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"The school year had been scheduled to begin more than a week ago ,","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"but Ferguson-Florissant district officials canceled classes last week","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"because of the unrest .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"Then they canceled school again Monday","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"they would try for next Monday .","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"`` We believe","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"that closing schools for the rest of this week will allow needed time","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"for peace and stability to be restored to our community","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"and allow families to plan ahead for the additional days","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"that children will be out of school , ''","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"school officials said in a written statement .","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"Businesses are hurting .","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"Kathleen Osborn , executive director of the Regional Business Council in the St. Louis area , said","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"about 25 businesses have been directly damaged by violence , many more simply by fear","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"that is keeping many residents from leaving their homes .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"`` The tragedy of it is that we are talking about small businesses , ''","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"she told .","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"`` Yet they are extraordinarily resilient .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"Some of these business owners get up in the morning ,","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"clean up their damage","depth":13},{"id":167,"text":"and open their stores .","depth":13},{"id":168,"text":"The problem is that you ca n't get them fully back in order","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"until you know","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"there wo n't be any more damage . ''","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"Many protesters realize","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"the violence has to stop .","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"Monday night , a group of people","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"trying to keep the peace","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"locked arms","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"and positioned themselves between the more confrontational protesters and the police line .","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"However ,","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"while many among the protesters clamored for calm ,","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"some in the crowd appeared determined to provoke an incident .","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"Johnson said","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"some of those arrested were from as far as New York and California","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"- part of what he called `` a dangerous dynamic of the night . ''","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"Of 78 arrests , only four were Ferguson residents .","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"Many were from the surrounding area .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"Eighteen were from out of state .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"`` Our peaceful protesters are not the enemy , ''","depth":10},{"id":187,"text":"Johnson said .","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"`` Tonight we closed the roadway .","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"We allowed those","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"who come in peace","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"to walk the roadway . ''","depth":11}],"relatio